c173923cb7da0afe1c7","tid":1286110,"uid":67294,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T01:08:45.000Z","msg":"武漢人自己出左文宣啦<br />\n咪插手啦，有無見過台灣人幫香港搞文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"26363f411892ef2634f5b39a3962f4b28aaa3c4c","tid":1286110,"uid":7760,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T01:09:18.000Z","msg":"大佬77 個遊行好撚明確<br />\n咪撚搞啲咩武漢起義<br />\n依加香港人已經持久抗爭左一個月, 你搵啲野分散香港人個目光成件事就失焦<br />\n<br />\n你要搞武漢野 你分開另一日搞"},{"pid":"e1b615cedfa6e6c598c2a87f19b5b341af0dd013","tid":1286110,"uid":125168,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T01:09:40.000Z","msg":"再搞就失焦"},{"pid":"7d76d15e679b2be60be95aa1b54fd7b4629ac3a8","tid":1286110,"uid":15032,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T01:11:09.000Z","msg":"收手啦 搞香港啦"},{"pid":"ccb75f55ece12925782cc5283d11832ba0e7764b","tid":1286110,"uid":85803,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T01:34:31.000Z","msg":"5大訴求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eea010ac54e85bee86449686c0064f44d8099243","tid":1286110,"uid":270179,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T06:58:42.000Z","msg":"唔好俾人分化到<br />\n冇人話要反攻大陸<br />\n只係要燒佢後欄<br />\n不割席<br />\n不篤灰<br />\n不沉船<br />\n兄弟爬山，各有各做，互相支援<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求缺一不可<br />\n1.撤回條例<br />\n2.釋放義士<br />\n3.取消暴動定性<br />\n4.追究警方濫用武力鎮壓<br />\n5.落實雙普選<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HtoEwdk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHtoEwdk.png&h=45ccf763&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Np0Z6F.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Np0Z6F.png&h=d451cb32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/05/145107_1568e89c3160c354acbc9eda8c078eee.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F05%2F145107_1568e89c3160c354acbc9eda8c078eee.png&h=2adf7012&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"15880f6b72497f0ccbfbc66030870041200eda1c","tid":1286110,"uid":14328,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:00:41.000Z","msg":"NICE"},{"pid":"bd53ef04a0214fb70b34ad989fe53a3a0bfb6e8b","tid":1286110,"uid":210682,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"9236172fd6a501c75df9ec173923cb7da0afe1c7","tid":1286110,"uid":67294,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T01:08:45.000Z","msg":"武漢人自己出左文宣啦<br />\n咪插手啦，有無見過台灣人幫香港搞文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:01:44.000Z","msg":"全香港人都知香港發生咩事，<br />\n但係咪全中國人都知武漢發生咩事？<br />\n香港冇封鎖消息但中國有，<br />\n所以你嘅類比好差"},{"pid":"cfae078b2540164e2b0734c2ef78e237e1ca29b6","tid":1286110,"uid":198175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:01:58.000Z","msg":"而家玩5大訴求+1?"},{"pid":"c4b22d98fdcc0bbaf89f3696f87b68af44f1840e","tid":1286110,"uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:02:57.000Z","msg":"關香港人撚事咩<br />\n咪撚搞埋啲無謂野啦屌"},{"pid":"4c86767c99b108e00d13b348f9671b7f6c0eaa7b","tid":1286110,"uid":209318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:04:41.000Z","msg":"你要搞自己上去武漢起義起飽佢"},{"pid":"606d1aa94fcdea1c59f9ed09469f8b3cbd7a223b","tid":1286110,"uid":69696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:05:54.000Z","msg":"支那人本性用完即棄，你幫完佢轉頭屌柒你，咁多年都唔明？"},{"pid":"e69d0b9a51c0bc12277d08f602959c791c59d36a","tid":1286110,"uid":76745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:05:54.000Z","msg":"負評 block 上一頁"},{"pid":"6fb7f09acb86d4105ab3d2ba6e916c26ba2f1cd5","tid":1286110,"uid":264457,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:08:29.000Z","msg":"第一種：沒用，印象差既２００百萬已用腳投左票。親中既點都親中，有生意既點都要做。<br />\n<br />\n第二種：中國人最叻就自掃門前雪，「我係來開心消費既，武漢我關咩事？」<br />\n<br />\n第三種：世界咁大，武漢呢啲都係落後國家常見之事，ＷＦＣ<br />\n<br />\n香港點解有西方報呀？因為有知名度咋，因為有價值。<br />\n你想搞武漢既就搵第日搞，宜家唔好騎劫個主題啦"}]}